item.title: Technical Specs
item.description: This site is created by hand from the ground up and is optimised for speed and simplicity. It uses a strack of Hugo as a static site generator and is hosted on Netlify. The website is set in the following fonts: Stix Two by MicroPress Type Foundry Comfortaa by Johan Aakerlund both under distributed under SIL Open Font Licence. Lander page feature Multi-Scale Turing Patterns based on Jonathan McCabe’s paper
